How to install Java on Windows:

1. 
java jdk download
https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#jdk19-windows
Install x64_bin.

2. Set path 
1. Look for "Edit the system environment variables" > Advanced > "Environment Variables"
2. In the System Variables, select the "Path" option and then clic on Edit... button.

3. Clic on the new button and past the copied link of the java installed:
C:\Program Files\Java\jdk-x\bin

4. Move up and then clic ok and ok.

5. Open Command prompt:
Type java -version and jshell -version


How to install Java on Mac:
1. 
java jdk download
https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#jdk19-windows
Install macOS Installer

2. Follow the installer steps

3. Launch terminal and type: java -version and jshell -version





